lyrics.line: Hak waa thoe phaan maa
Dai yin phleng ni
Khat waa thoe ko khong ruu dii
Waa pen chan
Mop hai thoe khon diao
At mai kiao tae samkhan
Phro chan
Nan yaak hai thoe dai fang
Thii fao tae thoh
Thoh pai haa thoe rueai pueai
Nuai ko yom
Ko jai chop thoe mai bao
Tae jai chao kam mai ruu loei
Waa thoe mai chop rao
Mai son lae mai ao
Mai yaak khui
Ko loei maa rong phleng bok
Kae yaak hai thoe nan jai
Ai sing thii chan tham long pai, jai sang maa
Yaa krot loei na khon dii
Yok thot hai chan na kaeo taa
Khrao lang ja mai maa, ja mai thoh
Ko loei maa rong phleng bok
Kae yaak hai thoe nan khao jai
Ai sing thii chan tham long pai, jai sang maa
Yaa krot loei na khon dii
Yok thot hai chan na kaeo taa
Khrao lang ja mai maa, ja thoh
Lae sutthai thii nai hua jai
Man ram rong
Yaak ja mong, ja mong naa thoe
Eek sak thii
Kon ja laa thoe pai
Khon jai dam naa taa dii
Khotot thoe sak thii jaak hua jai
Tae mii nueng kham
Thii yang khaang khaang nai
Kham phut luk phu chai
Chan chop thoe
